{"title":"看水大嫂（外一首）","authors":["李晓白"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"看水大嫂（外一首）\t李晓白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电门一扳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水车叫唤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井台是课桌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指头笔一杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日推水车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天要管电；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没水难丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没文化怎当社员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个生字写五遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要咬碎，要嚼烂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风徐徐吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫不落她头上汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水花似甘露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田禾露出笑颜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生字开花在心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从她脸上能看见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪管下工铃急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假装没有听见；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书页嗦嗦响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮子哗哗转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图书发行员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑一担文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈步儿来到深山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手帕汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脑子路线："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王家岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天有会；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李家沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜校明天开班；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对，还得去刘庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给三娘送一本《养鸡》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给二弟送一份《中国青年》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仔细一算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路儿百里远；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖抖肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是一副千斤担！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步扫风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心是策马鞭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指向科学岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上文化山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担子越闪越高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真像一支"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载运卫星的火箭！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}